DevOps doesn’t only bring together the development and operation processes of a business, it creates a central hub with an agile system where development and operations can work together effectively. The DevOps role has become paramount to scaling production and increasing the speed of development and iterations.

This DevOps test evaluates candidates’ ability to administer and troubleshoot Linux operating systems, understand and apply core programming concepts, paradigms, and patterns, improve an IT infrastructure using infrastructure as code and cloud computing principles, and implement DevOps practices and principles inside your organization.
